>> time required: 1 hour
>> course: breakfast

Mix @flour{1%cup}, @salt{1/4%tsp}, @melted butter{2%Tbsp} and @eggs{2 large} together in a bowl.

Gradually add the @milk{1/2%cup} and @water{1/2%cup} to the mixture.

Heat up a #pan or skillet{} over medium-high heat.

Lower heat to medium-low and begin laddling 1/3 cup scoops into the pan.

Cook until lightly browned on the bottom, flip, and continue until done on both sides.

Makes ~ 8 - 4 inch crepes. 
